text: RM2 or variant, may refer to: * RM2, the postcode for a part of Romford, see RM postcode area * Valmet RM 2, a class of two-bogie four-axle tram * Mendoza RM2, a light machine gun from Mexico * RocketMotorTwo (RM2), a Tier-1b rocket engine for SpaceShipTwo * RM2, a cancelled space station Russian Research Module * RM2, a type of railcar in the NZR RM class ==See also== * RM (disambiguation) * RMII
title: RM2
